description.value:
From OlofNi: 

Hi all,

We have now had an inital meeting for the change of logistics partner that DE needs by end of Q1 next year.

Some things that need clarity for all of you:

The change is driven by DE. As such, they are the PM (names to be provided). Scoping, budget and timeline is their responsibility.

Having said that, we are all stakeholders in some shape or form here and need to oversee the implementation throughtout.

DE requested a meeting on-site already next week but have now agreed to postpone that to the 19th-20th of the week after.

In that meeting, we will need stakeholder participation as far as possible. The purpose is to nail down a more detailed scope based on DEs requirments. Bogleboo have agreed to be on-site, but we will need representation from Entiros as well. 

@Mikael please verify possibility of attendance here. 

Again, let me re-iterate for clarity: this initiative is NOT driven and coordinated by GANT AB IT, but by DE as a partner to us.

More details to follow.

Kind Regards
